    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Traditional Mexican sandals having the uppers made of interwoven leather strips and often held on the foot by loose heel straps.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
